
/* --------------------------------------------------
The core logical processing:

   main
    |
->accept
|   |
|   |fork
|___|  \
        \
        recv:  <<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<< Client request
         |
      request
         |
         |fork
         |  \
         |   \-----"cgi"
         |           |
       read <-pipe- stdin
         |
      respond
         |
       send:  >>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>> respond Client

-------------------------------------------------- */
